data.description: MULTIPLE OFFERERS RECEIVED! PLEASE SUBMIT HIGHEST AND BEST BY DEC 20TH AT 5PM.  Investors special in a great location. This house is a must see with tons of potential!  4 beds 2.5 bath  2 living areas, enclosed attached Florida room (billiard room), converted garage, enclosed attached laundry room, 2 driveways, and additional RV parking on the side of the house.  This home is roughly 2700 sqft with "grandfathered" in additions. Seller is highly motivated.
